Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.10,0:00:12.30,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,I still remember it like it was yesterday,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.40,0:00:15.30,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,though it was countless moons ago
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.50,0:00:18.15,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,After he was defeated,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.60,0:00:21.05,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,not much of our once beautiful home was left
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.60,0:00:23.95,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,And the two brave ones that stood up for us all
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.20,0:00:25.80,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,ruled Equestria from then on
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.65,0:00:29.75,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,One day, the younger one, saddened by our daily struggles,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.15,0:00:31.90,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,proposed to form a new colony
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.60,0:00:35.45,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,where all of us would grow strong and happy
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.40,0:00:38.15,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,But the elder one forbade it,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.70,0:00:41.80,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,for she felt that it would divide and shatter the weakened kingdom
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.20,0:00:42.85,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,forever
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.85,0:00:45.75,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Nopony knows that we're still here,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.10,0:00:47.55,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,smiling beneath the moonlight
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.15,0:00:49.85,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,while remembering our dear mother,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.35,0:00:51.50,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,for we will forever be...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.20,0:00:54.50,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,her children of the night
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.80,0:01:23.05,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Come little children, I'll take thee away
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.55,0:01:28.90,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Into a land of enchantment
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.30,0:01:34.80,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Come little children, the time's come to play
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.10,0:01:40.75,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Here in my garden of sha-a-adows
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.50,0:01:57.55,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Follow sweet children, I'll show thee the way
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.15,0:02:03.50,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Through all the pain and the sorrows
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.90,0:02:09.25,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Weep not poor children, for life is this way
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.60,0:02:14.70,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Murdering beauty and passions
